<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Medicine Cards - Part 13</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f5f7fa;
      }
      .container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
      }
      .card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.2s;
      }
      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
      }
      .icon {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #007bff;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      h3 {
        margin: 10px 0 5px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
      p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #555;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Medicine Cards - Part 13</h1>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-dna"></i></div>
        <h3>Levosimendan</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Heart failure.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Calcium sensitizer, improves cardiac contractility.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-capsules"></i></div>
        <h3>Nintedanib (Ofev)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Tyrosine kinase inhibitor. Oral capsule.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-flask"></i></div>
        <h3>Macitentan (Opsumit)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Pulmonary arterial hypertension.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Endothelin receptor antagonist.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-heartbeat"></i></div>
        <h3>Ambrisentan (Letairis)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Pulmonary arterial hypertension.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Oral ERA, improves exercise capacity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-syringe"></i></div>
        <h3>Galsulfase (Naglazyme)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Mucopolysaccharidosis VI.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Enzyme replacement therapy. IV infusion.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-vial"></i></div>
        <h3>Elosulfase alfa (Vimizim)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> MPS IVA.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Enzyme replacement therapy for Morquio A syndrome.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-disease"></i></div>
        <h3>Velmanase alfa (Lamzede)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Alpha-mannosidosis.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Recombinant human enzyme therapy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-dna"></i></div>
        <h3>Idursulfase (Elaprase)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Hunter syndrome (MPS II).</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Enzyme replacement therapy. IV infusion.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-prescription"></i></div>
        <h3>Laronidase (Aldurazyme)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Hurler & Scheie syndromes (MPS I).</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Enzyme replacement therapy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-flask"></i></div>
        <h3>Asfotase alfa (Strensiq)</h3>
        <p><strong>Indication:</strong> Hypophosphatasia.</p>
        <p><strong>Details:</strong> Enzyme replacement for rare metabolic bone disease.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
